_sText:
This map was made for the "Comic Book Deathrun" Mapping contest on GameBanana


Background:
This map was designed for a mapping contest for GameBanana. The map contains many custom textures to help the visual style of the map. The there three levels to this map. Each level has many obstacles that progressively get harder and harder.

Support:
Cubemaps, FPS (Hints/Skips, Area Protals,Func_occluder), Custom Textures, Spawnpoints (48)CT and (3)T = 51 Total

Custom:
